Brujeria - Viva Presidente Trump! (Single)2016 ak320

Brujeria is an extreme metal band formed in Tijuana, Mexico in 1989. Their name comes from the Spanish word for "witchcraft". Their songs, which are sung entirely in Spanish, are focused on Satanism, anti-Christianity, sex, immigration, narcotics smuggling, politics and also include lyrics about killing white people (despite having a vast majority of white members in the band).
Brujeria are  a side-project of guitarist Dino Cazares (founding member of Fear Factory), and has featured  Billy Gould, Nicholas Barker, Raymond Herrera, Jeff Walker and Shane Embury. They portray themselves as a Latino band consisting of drug lords, concealing their identities due to being wanted by the FBI.
